title: Australian diary. No. 122
brief_description: Magazine items: The Australian Consumers’ Association test on the durability of children’s shoes; a display in South Australia for prospective buyers and pilots of light aircraft; a dazzling exhibition by Horace lindrum, last of five generations of Lindrums, all of whom have proved masters on the billiard table.
